quran[51]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Tọ̄ sīn mīm
  26,2,Ìwọ̀nyí ni àwọn āyah Tírà t’ó ń yanjú ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀dá
  26,3,Nítorí kí ni o ṣe máa para rẹ pé wọn kò jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo
  26,4,"Tí A bá fẹ́, A máa sọ àmì kan kalẹ̀ fún wọn láti sánmọ̀. Àwọn ọrùn wọn kò sì níí yé tẹríba fún un"
  26,5,Kò sí ìrántí kan tí ó máa dé bá wọn ní titun láti ọ̀dọ̀ Àjọkẹ́-ayé àfi kí wọ́n jẹ́ olùgbúnrí kúrò níbẹ̀
  26,6,"Dájúdájú wọ́n ti pe (āyah Wa) nírọ́. Nítorí náà, àwọn ìró ohun tí wọ́n ń fi ṣe yẹ̀yẹ́ ń bọ̀ wá bá wọn"
  26,7,Ṣé wọn kò rí ilẹ̀ pé mélòó mélòó nínú gbogbo oríṣiríṣi n̄ǹkan alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé tí A mú hù jáde láti inú rẹ̀
  26,8,Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn kò jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo
  26,9,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun mà ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  26,10,"(Rántí) nígbà tí Olúwa rẹ pe (Ànábì) Mūsā pé: \"Lọ bá ìjọ alábòsí"
  26,11,ìjọ Fir‘aon (kí o sì sọ̱ fún wọn) pé 'Ṣé wọn kò níí bẹ̀rù (Allāhu) ni
  26,12,"Ó sọ pé: \"Olúwa mi, dájúdájú èmi ń bẹ̀rù pé wọ́n máa pè mí ní òpùrọ́"
  26,13,"Ó sì máa jẹ́ ìnira fún mi (tí wọ́n bá pè mí ní òpùrọ́). Ahọ́n mi kò sì já gaaraga. Nítorí náà, ránṣẹ́ sí Hārūn"
  26,14,"Àti pé mo ní ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ kan lọ́rùn lọ́dọ̀ wọn. Nítorí náà, mò ń bẹ̀rù pé wọ́n máa pa mí"
  26,15,"(Allāhu) sọ pé: \"Rárá (wọn kò lè pa ọ́). Nítorí náà, kí ẹ̀yin méjèèjì mú àwọn àmì (iṣẹ́ ìyanu) Wa lọ (bá wọn). Dájúdájú Àwa ń bẹ pẹ̀lú yín; À ń gbọ́ (ọ̀rọ̀ yín)"
  26,16,"Ẹ̀yin méjèèjì, ẹ lọ bá Fir‘aon. Kí ẹ sọ fún un pé: 'Dájúdájú àwa ni Òjíṣẹ́ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá"
  26,17,(À ń sọ fún ọ) pé kí o jẹ́ kí àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl máa bá wa lọ
  26,18,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Ṣé kì í ṣe ní ààrin wa ni a ti tọ́ ọ ní kékeré ni, tí o sì gbé ní ọ̀dọ̀ wa fún ọdún púpọ̀ nínú ìṣẹ̀mí ayé rẹ"
  26,19,O sì ṣe iṣẹ́ ọwọ́ rẹ tí o ṣe (sí wa). Ìwọ sì wà nínú àwọn aláìmoore.”
  26,20,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: \"Mo ṣe é nígbà náà nígbà tí mo wà nínú àwọn aláìmọ̀kan ni"
  26,21,"Mo sì sá fun yín nígbà tí mo bẹ̀rù yín. Nítorí náà, Allāhu ti ta mí lọ́rẹ ipò Ànábì. Ó sì ṣe mí ní (ọ̀kan) nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́"
  26,22,Àti pé ìyẹn ni ìdẹ̀ra tí ò ń ṣe ìrègún rẹ̀ lé mi lórí. Pé ó sọ àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl di ẹrú (ńkọ́)
  26,23,"Fir‘aon wí pé: “Kí ni Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá?”"
  26,24,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “(Allāhu ni)"
  26,25,"(Fir‘aon) wí fún àwọn t’ó wà ní àyíká rẹ̀ pé: “Ṣé ẹ ẹ̀ gbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ (t’ó ń sọ ni)?”"
  26,26,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “(Allāhu ni) Olúwa yín àti Olúwa àwọn bàbá yín, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́.”"
  26,27,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Dájúdájú Òjíṣẹ́ yín èyí tí wọ́n rán si yín, wèrè mà ni.”"
  26,28,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “(Allāhu ni) Olúwa ibùyọ òòrùn, ibùwọ̀ òòrùn àti ohunkóhun t’ó ń bẹ láààrin àwọn méjèèjì, tí ẹ bá máa ń ṣe làákàyè.”"
  26,29,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Dájúdájú tí o bá fi lè jọ́sìn fún ọlọ́hun kan yàtọ̀ sí mi, dájúdájú mo máa sọ ọ́ di ara àwọn ẹlẹ́wọ̀n.”"
  26,30,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé mo mú kiní kan t’ó yanjú wá fún ọ ńkọ́?”"
  26,31,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Mú un wá nígbà náà tí ìwọ bá wà nínú àwọn olódodo.”"
  26,32,"Nítorí náà, ó ju ọ̀pá rẹ̀ sílẹ̀, ó sì di ejò pọ́nńbélé"
  26,33,"Ó tún fa ọwọ́ rẹ̀ yọ síta, ó sì di funfun fún àwọn olùwòran"
  26,34,"(Fir‘aon) wí fún àwọn ìjòyè tí wọ́n wà ní àyíká rẹ̀ pé: “Dájúdájú èyí ni onímọ̀ nípa idán pípa"
  26,35,Ó fẹ́ ko yín kúrò lórí ilẹ̀ yín ni. Kí ni ohun tí ẹ máa mú wá ní ìmọ̀ràn?”
  26,36,"Wọ́n wí pé: \"Dá òun àti arákùnrin rẹ̀ dúró ná, kí o sì rán àwọn akónijọ sí àwọn ìlú"
  26,37,(pé) kí gbogbo onímọ̀ nípa idán pípa wá bá ọ
  26,38,Wọ́n sì kó àwọn òpìdán jọ ní àsìkò tí wọ́n fi àdéhùn sí ní ọjọ́ tí (gbogbo ìlú) ti mọ̀
  26,39,"Wọ́n sì wí fún àwọn ènìyàn pé: \"Ṣé ẹ̀yin máa kó jọ (síbẹ̀) bí"
  26,40,Nítorí kí á lè tẹ̀lé àwọn òpìdán tí ó bá jẹ́ pé àwọn ni olùborí
  26,41,"Nígbà tí àwọn òpìdán dé, wọ́n wí fún Fir‘aon pé: “Ǹjẹ́ owó-ọ̀yà kan wà fún wa, tí ó bá jẹ́ pé àwa gan-an la jẹ́ olùborí?”"
  26,42,"(Fir‘aon) wí pé: “Bẹ́ẹ̀ ni, dájúdájú nígbà náà ẹ máa wà nínú àwọn alásùn-únmọ́ (mi).”"
  26,43,"(Ànábì) Mūsā sọ fún wọn pé: “Ẹ ju ohun tí ẹ fẹ́ jù sílẹ̀.”"
  26,44,"Wọ́n sì ju àwọn okùn wọn àti ọ̀pá wọn sílẹ̀. Wọ́n wí pé: “Pẹ̀lú ògo Fir‘aon, dájúdájú àwa, àwa ni olùborí.”"
  26,45,"Nígbà náà, (Ànábì) Mūsā ju ọ̀pá rẹ̀ sílẹ̀. Ó sì ń gbé ohun tí wọ́n pa nírọ́ kalẹ̀ mì kálókáló"
  26,46,"Nítorí náà, iṣẹ́ ìyanu (Ànábì Mūsā) mú àwọn òpìdán wó lulẹ̀, tí wọ́n forí kanlẹ̀ (fún Allāhu)"
  26,47,"Wọ́n sọ pé: \"A gbàgbọ́ nínú Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá"
  26,48,Olúwa (Ànábì) Mūsā àti Hārūn
  26,49,"Fir‘aon wí pé: “Ẹ gbà Á gbọ́ ṣíwájú kí n̄g tó yọ̀ǹda fun yín! Dájúdájú òun ni àgbà yín tí ó kọ yín ní idán pípa. Láìpẹ́ ẹ̀ ń bọ̀ wá mọ̀. Dájúdájú mo máa gé ọwọ́ yín àti ẹsẹ̀ yín ní ìpasípayọ. Lẹ́yìn náà, dájúdájú mo máa kan gbogbo yín mọ́gi.”"
  26,50,"(Àwọn òpìdán) sọ pé: “Kò sí ìnira fún wa! Dájúdájú àwa yó sì fàbọ̀ sí ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wa"
  26,51,Dájúdájú àwa n retí pé Olúwa wa yóò ṣe àforíjìn àwọn àṣìṣe wa fún wa nítorí pé àwa jẹ́ ẹni àkọ́kọ́ (tí ó jẹ́) onígbàgbọ́ òdodo.”